  <div class="ProfileHeaderCard">
  <h1 class="ProfileHeaderCard-name">
    <a href="/Kuldip4Telford" class="ProfileHeaderCard-nameLink u-textInheritColor js-nav">Cllr Kuldip Sahota</a>
  </h1>

  <h2 class="ProfileHeaderCard-screenname u-inlineBlock u-dir" dir="ltr">
    <a class="ProfileHeaderCard-screennameLink u-linkComplex js-nav" href="/Kuldip4Telford">
      <span class="username u-dir" dir="ltr">@<b class="u-linkComplex-target">Kuldip4Telford</b></span>
    </a>
  </h2>

  

      <p class="ProfileHeaderCard-bio u-dir" dir="ltr">Kuldip Sahota, borough Cllr for Malinslee &amp; Dawley Bank. Campaigner, community activist &amp; business owner. Top priority is saving hospital services at PRH.</p>

      <div class="ProfileHeaderCard-location ">
        <span class="Icon Icon--geo Icon--medium" aria-hidden="true" role="presentation"></span>

              Telford, England

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Great to hear from three strong Labour women from <a href="/wrekinlabour" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="1425122155"><s>@</s><b>wrekinlabour</b></a>  come to speak to <a href="/Telfordlabour" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="1080905119"><s>@</s><b>Telfordlabour</b></a> all members meeting. <div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">Can someone, anyone remind <a href="/TelfordTories" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="2316946518"><s>@</s><b>TelfordTories</b></a> that an opposition has a responsibility to provide an alternative budget not just take pot-shots.
<a href="/hashtag/YouHadOneJob?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>YouHadOneJob</b></a><a href="https://t.co/RCcI5AxxtS" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/telfordlabour/status/969282311261999104" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/telfordlabour/status/969282311261999104"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/telfordlabour/</span><span class="invisible">status/969282311261999104</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>

      <li class="embed-link js-actionEmbedTweet" data-nav="embed_tweet">
        <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Embed Tweet</button>
      </li>
  </ul>
</div>

</div>

  </div>

      </div>

      

      


      
        <div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Edith Picton-Turbervill
It was social and philanthropic work which drew her to the labour movement, leading her to conclude that 'fundamental changes in law were necessary to obtain better conditions of life for the people.
The Wrekins first woman MP.<a href="https://t.co/jCwpgk90Uz" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/jCwpgk90Uz</a></p>
</div>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Two teams out today campaigning for David Wright in St. Georges.

A big show of support from residents for David who are concerned with the Tories austerity and systematic destruction of the NHS.

<a href="/hashtag/davewright4stgeorges?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>davewright4stgeorges</b></a> on March 15th.
<a href="/hashtag/labourdoorstep?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>labourdoorstep</b></a><a href="https://t.co/LW8aE28vSM" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/LW8aE28vSM</a></p>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">A busy morning for <a href="/Telfordlabour" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="1080905119"><s>@</s><b>telfordlabour</b></a>
Today we started campaigning for David Wright in the <a href="/hashtag/stgeorges?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>stgeorges</b></a> by-election.

Great turn out from a number of volunteer groups all getting the Labour message out to local residents.
<a href="/hashtag/labourdoorstep?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>labourdoorstep</b></a> <a href="/hashtag/votedavidwright?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>votedavidwright</b></a><a href="https://t.co/csDJyicdWu" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/csDJyicdWu</a></p>

        <div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Today the chairs of <a href="/Telfordlabour" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="1080905119"><s>@</s><b>telfordlabour</b></a> and <a href="/wrekinlabour" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="1425122155"><s>@</s><b>wrekinlabour</b></a>  have written to our MP's. 

The letter highlights the devastating truth; the Tories have prioritised tax giveaways for the privileged few, public services like our NHS have paid the price and we call on our MPs to take action.<a href="https://t.co/H5yoQ1BNAJ" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/H5yoQ1BNAJ</a></p>

    <div class="caret-outer"></div>
    <div class="caret-inner"></div>
  </div>
  <ul>
    
      <li class="copy-link-to-tweet js-actionCopyLinkToTweet">

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">This morning <a href="/CllrShaunDavies" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="53358128"><s>@</s><b>CllrShaunDavies</b></a> was on <a href="/BBCShropshire" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="40880876"><s>@</s><b>BBCShropshire</b></a>. Talking about the councils finances and how the government cuts to local council funding are hitting Telford &amp; Wrekin's budgeting. 
You can listen to the interview below, starting at 2:07 into the show.<a href="https://t.co/CMwAmfh8Yx" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p05qyq12" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p05qyq12"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">http://www.</span><span class="js-display-url">bbc.co.uk/programmes/p05</span><span class="invisible">qyq12</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">The Jackfield Stabilisation project has been shortlisted for the <a href="/hashtag/civilengineerspeopleschoiceawards?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>civilengineerspeopleschoiceawards</b></a>

<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">Under Labour, extra tax you'll pay if you earn...
14k = 0
20k = 0
26k = 0
35k = 0
75k (!) = 0
100,000 = 1,000
500,000 = 22,925<a href="https://t.co/KwTdSNl8Oq" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/uklabour/status/865630395710062594" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/uklabour/status/865630395710062594"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/uklabour/statu</span><span class="invisible">s/865630395710062594</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
